channel.title: Not existing item? :S
channel.description:
Hello folks, I'm playing on DeltaScape atm and when I tried to spawn a bandos godsword (added to client) it says NOT EXISTING ITEM when I weild it. Could anyone please tell me how to "add" the item, or something?
Thanks ~ Extoz

item.title: Not existing item? :S
item.dc:creator: @legend-scape legend-scape
item.description:
@legend-scape wrote:

[quote=“Rog3r, post:3, topic:239708”]Means your Item.cfg doesn’t have that item ID.

I suggest the items you wish to add in your server, first add them in Item.Java

I know your client supports it, if it didn’t, it would come up as null.
Just a simple fix. ;)[/quote]

yh ty rog3r :P,
